
External Requirements:
----------------------
libxml2
wxWidgets (wxGTK)
 - gentoo: eselect wxwidgets show|list


Lib requirements included:
--------------------------
>=gsoap-2.7.14
zlib
net-snmp
>=openssl-0.9.8k
>=wxGTK-2.8.10.1-r5


Installation:
-------------

1. First build the source tree. The install requires the source 
   package is first built AND cleaned, so run 
    $ make && make clean 
   as a user who has local write privileges.


2. Create arch configurations in config/environment/$TNMS_ENV/`hostname`/
   This assumes we have a desired server arch. in mind.
    

3. Create a system account for the tnms environment and install the 
   binaries.

    $ export TNMS_ENV="dev"
    $ export ROLEUSER="tnms"
    $ sudo useradd -d /opt/tnms -m -U -s /sbin/nologin $ROLEUSER
    $ sudo -u $ROLEUSER -H /bin/bash 
    $   #(from the root tnms src tree as $ROLEUSER)
    $ source config/scripts/tnmsrc
    $ source config/environment/$TNMS_ENV/bashrc
    $ make install


3. Initialize the database configurations.

    $ ./bin/tnms_dbinit.sh -D tnmsauthd -U tnmsauth -P tnmsauth11b -x tca -p
    $ ./bin/ta_dbinit.sh fwlr
    $ ./bin/ta_dbinit.sh tnms


4. Add agents to authdb.

    $ tnms_useradd -A -u fwlr/nebula -g tnmsagents -m dbstatic



